            <title>[KAFKA-542] Upgrade to metrics 3.x</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-542</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;metrics 3.0.0 fixes some issues with the csv reporter that affect 0.8&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;E.g., with metrics 2.1.3 we would just have NumDelayedRequests.csv but with 3.0.0 we would have kafka.server.ProducerRequestPurgatory.NumDelayedRequests.csv and kafka.server.FetchRequestPurgatory.NumDelayedRequests.csv&lt;/p&gt;</description>
